  "body": "I tried a crowdsale with Standard token. When i call the buyToken methods using ganache-cli as the network, it works fine, but when i repeat the same with geth, it fails.\r\n\r\nI found the root cause to be,\r\n\r\ntoken.safeTransfer line in crowdsale.sol\r\n\r\nIt redirects to SageERC20.sol which in turn should call the transfer method in BasicToken.sol\r\n\r\nWhich will return true if success.\r\n\r\nBut when i call this method, it fails.\r\n\r\nBut the method doesnot have any issue, i even tried commenting out all lines in the method and returned true, still it fails",
